com.gembox.spreadsheet

Class WorksheetProtection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gembox.spreadsheet.WorksheetProtection

  • public final class WorksheetProtection
extends Object
    Protection settings. Supported in XLSX only.

    Fields in this class are simply written to Excel file and have no effect on the behavior of this library. For more information on worksheet protection, consult Microsoft Excel documentation.

      • setPasswordHash

        public void setPasswordHash(int passwordHash)
        Sets the password hash for protected sheet.

        This field needs to be set to value smaller than Short.MAX_VALUE * 2. For setting password it can be also used setPassword(java.lang.String) method.
